== Attention admin ==
The reason the user files were getting fucked up is I was tired and made a typo when editing the config file. 
Fixed version is here http://127.0.0.1:43110/1HamXwKoauiykRmVLrQxDVjRGoVZX7ngkE
Posting zip files won't work if you just try the code locally - all clients need to be running it or it will hang on "processing".
To install just copy the js files from that site's dist folder.
People are welcome to try uploading files with obscure extensions to test it, or at least click on it and wait until it loads to begin seeding it.
